Text: Fw K Race PredictorsHi Kenyan runners here is some useful information concerning the k this week end and what pace you should run You should run the first K at that pace then pick up if possible the second K Marine Corps New York or San Antonio should use the faster sheet All other runners use the slower sheet Thanks JonSeanJerry
